channel.title: Making myself an owner on a 718/742
channel.description:
I'm having trouble making myself an owner on "Reduction 718/742".
Other's were having trouble giving themselves owner privileges but they figured it out. I on the other hand, did not. I'm not a noob at this, but it's not as simple as just changing the previous owners name (which I already did). If anyone could help that would be amazing.
I wish the source came with a control panel.. Anyone know how I can make/where I can get one?
It'd be easier to talk on skype so just message me: tylerpeterson45
Or, just post a reply to what you think I should do. Thanks!!
